```plantuml
@startuml kryptokrauts_ae-prediction-cards
actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Wallet Client" as WC
participant "PredictionCards API" as API
participant "Smart Contract" as SC
participant "Oracle Service" as OS
participant "Process Prediction Service" as PPS
participant "Aeternity Blockchain" as AE

User -> FE: Create Prediction
FE -> WC: Connect Wallet
WC -> AE: Authenticate
FE -> API: Submit Prediction
API -> SC: create_prediction()
SC -> AE: Store Prediction

User -> FE: Rent NFT
FE -> API: rent_nft()
API -> SC: rent_nft()
SC -> AE: Update NFT Rental

PPS -> SC: Monitor Predictions
SC -> PPS: Prediction Closed Event
PPS -> OS: Request Oracle Query
OS -> SC: ask_for_winning_option()
SC -> AE: Oracle Query
AE -> OS: Oracle Response
OS -> SC: process_oracle_response()
SC -> PPS: Winning Outcome
PPS -> SC: Update NFT Ownership

User -> FE: Claim Rewards
FE -> API: claim()
API -> SC: claim()
SC -> AE: Transfer Rewards

@enduml
```